David Kirkpatrick, author of "The 
Facebook Effect," says Twitter will be valued at about "one 
tenth" the size of Facebook when the company sells shares to the
public. Kirkpatrick talks with Bloomberg's  Tom Keene  and Sara 
Eisen on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg Surveillance."     (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:19
 